Class Decl

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Decl>, Node
public final class Decl
extends Decls

Represents a variable declaration, such as 'x : X'. Declarations are used with quantified formulas and comprehension expressions.

Author:
Emina Torlak
invariant:
variable.arity = expression.arity
children = variable + expression
specfield:

expression: Expression
